snippet.title: Atari XL/XE - Rescue on Fractalus [Lucasfilm Games] 1985
snippet.description:
Rescue on Fractalus from Lucasfilm Games in 1985.

Programmers : Loren Carpenter and David Fox.

Graphics Artists : Douglas Crowford, Charlie Kellner, James St. Louis and Gary Winnick.

Sounds : Charlie Kellner and Peter Langston

Intro and gameplay video of this fantastic game ! 
PAL Version.
